arts.ttl: KNVB Cup: Noordwijk stun Willem II as Ajax eventually see off Telstar
arts.sum: The KNVB Cup round of 32 concluded on Thursday with Ajax playing. Below is a round up of the action. Noordwijk 2-1 Willem II Amateur side Noordwijk stunned Willem II to reach the last 16. Willem II made changes for the match and they found themselves behind after only two minutes as Emiel Wendt netted.
